## Custom User-Defined Rules

Stored in DB as `CustomRecognizer`:
- `detection_method`: `"regex"` | `"keyword_list"` | `"llm_prompt"`
- `entity_type`: uppercase underscore (e.g., `PATIENT_FILE_NUMBER`)
- `context_words`: nearby words that boost confidence
- `placeholder_label`: e.g., `"PATIENT_FILE"` → `[PATIENT_FILE_1]`

