## NER Models — Language → Model Mapping

Configurable in Settings. Defaults:

| Language         | Model                                              |
|------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| English          | dslim/bert-base-NER                                |
| Turkish          | akdeniz27/xlm-roberta-base-turkish-ner             |
| German           | dbmdz/bert-large-cased-finetuned-conll03-german    |
| French           | Jean-Baptiste/roberta-large-ner-english            |
| Spanish          | mrm8488/bert-spanish-cased-finetuned-ner           |
| Dutch            | wietsedv/bert-base-dutch-cased-finetuned-ner       |
| Chinese          | uer/roberta-base-finetuned-cluener2020-chinese     |
| Arabic           | hatmimoha/arabic-ner-bert                          |
| Russian          | DeepPavlov/rubert-base-cased-ner                   |
| Portuguese       | malduwais/biobert-base-cased-v1.2-finetuned-ner    |
| Japanese         | cl-tohoku/bert-base-japanese                       |
| Multilingual     | Babelscape/wikineural-multilingual-ner             |
| Fallback         | Babelscape/wikineural-multilingual-ner             |

Models load lazily and are cached in memory.

