## National ID Validators

Algorithmic checksum validation in `services/national_ids/`:

| Country       | ID Type    | Algorithm                          |
|---------------|------------|------------------------------------|
| Turkey        | TCKN       | 11-digit, custom checksum (d10,d11)|
| USA           | SSN        | 3-2-4 format, area code blacklist  |
| Brazil        | CPF        | 11 digits, two-step Luhn           |
| India         | Aadhaar    | 12 digits, Verhoeff checksum       |
| China         | RIC        | 18 chars, GB11643 checksum         |
| South Korea   | RRN        | 13 digits, checksum mod 11         |
| Netherlands   | BSN        | 9 digits, 11-proef checksum        |
| Australia     | TFN        | 8-9 digits, weighted checksum      |
| Canada        | SIN        | 9 digits, Luhn algorithm           |
| Global        | IBAN       | ISO 7064 MOD 97-10                 |
| Global        | SWIFT/BIC  | ISO 9362 format validation         |

