## Supported Document Types

| Category     | Formats                          | Library                             |
|--------------|----------------------------------|-------------------------------------|
| Document     | .pdf                             | PyMuPDF (fitz)                      |
| Document     | .docx, .doc                      | python-docx + LibreOffice fallback  |
| Spreadsheet  | .xlsx, .xls, .ods, .csv, .tsv   | openpyxl, pandas, odfpy             |
| Presentation | .pptx, .ppt                      | python-pptx + LibreOffice fallback  |
| Image        | .png, .jpg, .jpeg, .tiff, .bmp   | PaddleOCR + OpenCV + Pillow         |
| Audio        | .mp3, .wav, .m4a, .ogg, .flac   | OpenAI Whisper (local, on-device)   |
| Web/Markup   | .html, .htm, .md, .markdown      | BeautifulSoup4, markdown-it-py      |
| Data         | .json, .yaml, .yml, .xml         | custom flattener, PyYAML, lxml      |
| Email        | .eml, .msg                       | email stdlib, extract-msg           |
| Text         | .txt, .rtf                       | direct, striprtf                    |
| eBook        | .epub                            | ebooklib + BeautifulSoup4           |
